	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Shooter game for the NES</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm looking for an NES game that meets the following conditions:<br /><br />A shooter game similar to &quot;Gradius&quot; that also plays in space and where you control a spaceship.<br />But a game that is not an arcade conversion or a conversion from another console or home computer. It needs to be a game that originally appeared on the NES. (If there are versions on other systems that are ports of the NES game, that would be fine.)<br />Also, it should not be a sequel of a game that was originally for the arcade.<br />And it should be quite known. So, not just some random game of the seemingly endless library of NES shooters that nobody has ever heard of. It should be a well-known game.<br /><br />Does anything like this exist?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


